<h2>How to run the app</h2> 
<p> On your local machine: </p>
<ul>
  <li>1. Open your terminal.</li>
  <li>2. Enter `git clone https://github.com/othman-19/only-members-nodejs`.</li>
  <li>3. Navigate to the cloned repository.</li>
  <li>4. In the terminal cd into Inventory-app-expressjs.</li>
  <li>5. Run `npm install` in your terminal.</li>
  <li>6. Run `npm run serverstart` or `DEBUG=only-members-nodejs:* npm run devstart` in your terminal.</li>
  <li>7. In your browser try this url: `http://localhost:3000/`.</li>
  <li>8. Try subscribe, create posts, become a member or an admin.</li>
</ul>
